name: [JIUN] [HOST COMMUNITY] [21&28 Dec Blast] - '23 Year-End Availability Reminder

parameters.query:
=SET TIMEZONE = 'Asia/Kuala_Lumpur';

with avai_listings as
(select distinct l.id, 
l.user_id as host_id,
count(distinct dates.ymd)as avai_days
from listings l 
left join users u on u.id = l.user_id 
left join listing_availability la on la.listing_id = l.id
left join listing_location ll on ll.listing_id = l.id
left join (SELECT generate_series(NOW()::timestamp, timestamp '2024-01-02', interval '1 day')::date ymd) dates 
on dates.ymd between la.start_date::date and la.end_date::date
where 1=1
and ll.country = 'Malaysia'
and l.status = 'approved'
and l.deleted_at is null
--and l.id = '20035'
group by 1,2),
--
active_listings as
(select distinct b.listing_id 
from bookings b 
left join listings l on l.id = b.listing_id 
left join listing_location ll on ll.listing_id = b.listing_id 
where 1=1
and b.status = 'completed'
and b.request_end_at between NOW() - interval '90 days' and NOW()
and ll.country = 'Malaysia'
order by 1), 
--
hosts as
(select distinct u.id, 
concat(u.first_name,' ',u.last_name)as host_name, 
u.email, 
u.phone_number,
u.uuid
from users u),
--
bad_host as
(select distinct l.id as listing_id, t.name as tag
from listings l 
left join tag_taggables tt on tt.taggable_id = l.id
left join tags t on t.id = tt.tag_id 
where t.name = 'Bad Host'),
--
listing_cohort as
(select av.id as listing_id,
h.*,
av.avai_days, 
ac.listing_id
from avai_listings av
left join active_listings ac on ac.listing_id = av.id
left join hosts h on h.id = av.host_id
left join bad_host bh on bh.listing_id = av.id
where 1=1
and ((av.avai_days <= '6' --0 avai days
and ac.listing_id is not null --L3Mactive cars
and bh.tag is null)
or 
(h.email = 'jiunyew98@gmail.com'))
)
--
select --lc.*
distinct lc.id as host_id, 
lc.host_name, 
lc.email, 
lc.uuid 
from listing_cohort lc
